---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import GalleryLightbox from '../../components/GalleryLightbox.astro';

const title = "Jewellery Brand — Social Media Visual System | Aenea";
const description = "A social media visual system by Aenea for a fine jewellery brand — a curated feed with ivory tones, soft shadows, and gold, art-directed for a consistent, recognisable atmosphere.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Navbar current="work" />

  <main>
    <section class="proj-intro wrap">
      <a href="/work" class="back-link"><span aria-hidden="true">←</span> Selected Work</a>
      <span class="eyebrow proj-cat">Social Visuals</span>
      <h1 class="proj-title">Jewellery Brand</h1>
      <p class="proj-lead">A social media visual system for a fine jewellery brand — designed to function as a curated feed, not a collection of posts, with one consistent atmosphere across the entire grid.</p>
      <div class="proj-meta">
        <div><div class="meta-k">Service</div><div class="meta-v">Social Visuals</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Sector</div><div class="meta-v">Jewellery &amp; Luxury</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Year</div><div class="meta-v">2025</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Deliverables</div><div class="meta-v">Art direction, Visual system, Templates</div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <figure class="bleed" data-lightbox>
      <img src="/jewellery-hero.jpg" alt="Jewellery brand social media visual system — curated feed art direction by Aenea" />
    </figure>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">01</span><span class="eyebrow">Overview</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>A social media visual system designed to function as a curated feed — not a collection of posts. Every frame is considered as part of a whole, so the brand reads as one continuous, intentional atmosphere.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="wrap">
      <div class="pair">
        <figure class="ph s7 r43" data-lightbox><img src="/jewellery-1.jpg" alt="Jewellery brand editorial still — social visual system by Aenea" /></figure>
        <figure class="ph s5 r45" data-lightbox><img src="/jewellery-2.jpg" alt="Jewellery brand product close-up with soft shadow and gold tones" /></figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">02</span><span class="eyebrow">The System</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>Ivory tones, soft shadows, and touches of gold establish a consistent visual temperature. Every image — product close-ups, editorial stills, abstract textures — is selected and directed to hold the same atmosphere across the entire grid.</p>
        <p>The approach is restrained by design. Visuals never compete with the jewellery; they frame it. Negative space does as much work as the subject itself.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="wrap">
      <div class="pair">
        <figure class="ph s5 r45" data-lightbox><img src="/jewellery-3.jpg" alt="Jewellery brand abstract texture frame" /></figure>
        <figure class="ph s7 r43" data-lightbox><img src="/jewellery-4.jpg" alt="Jewellery brand feed layout across multiple posts" /></figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">03</span><span class="eyebrow">Outcome</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>The result is a feed that feels intentional, recognisable, and brand-consistent — scroll after scroll. A system that keeps the brand unmistakably itself across every post.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="next wrap">
      <a href="/work/ai-imagery" class="next-link">
        <span class="next-k">Next project</span>
        <span class="next-title">AI Brand Imagery <span class="arr" aria-hidden="true">↗</span></span>
        <span class="next-cat">Art Direction</span>
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
  <GalleryLightbox />
</Layout>